<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>في ظَلاَمِ اللَّيْلِ تَسْعَى * أَسْفَلَ الجُدْرَانِ تَنْقُبْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَإِذَا أَحْسَسْتَ صَوْتَاً * فَإِلى جُحْرِكَ تَهْرَبْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَيُّهَا الصُّعْلُوكُ أَبْشِرْ * غَابَتِ الْقِطَّةُ فَالْعَبْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مَا هُوَ؟<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا شَيْءٌ إِذَا فَسَدَا * تحَوَّلَ غَيُّهُ رَشَدَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَإِن هُوَ ظَلَّ في دَعَةٍ * أَثَارَ الشَّرَّ حَيْثُ بَدَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ذَكِيُّ العِرْقِ وَالِدُهُ * وَلَكِنْ بِئْسَ مَا وَلَدَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>*********<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مَا هِيَ؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تُنَادِي طِفْلَكَ اجْعَلْني * كَأُمٍّ لاَ تَمِلْ عَنيِّ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَلاَ تَفْزَعْ كَمَأْخُوذٍ * مِنَ البَيْتِ إِلى السِّجْنِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>كَأَنِّي وَجْهُ صَيَّادٍ * وَأَنْتَ الطَّيرُ في الغُصْنِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَلاَ بُدَّ لَكَ اليَوْمَ * وَإِلاَّ فَغَدَاً مِنيِّ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أَوِ اسْتَغْنِ عَنِ العَقْلِ * إِذَن عَنيِّ سَتَسْتَغْني<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَنَا المِصْبَاحُ لِلْفِكْرِ * أَنَاْ المِفْتَاحُ لِلذِّهْنِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>